qPlurk
------

Simple Plurk Client using PyQt and unofficial plurk API by David Blume.

v0.10
-----
 - login to plurk
 - get plurks and user information
 - post a plurk
 - display all response for a specific plurk
 - post a response for a specific plurk
 - emoticon support ( no restriction to use any emoticon, but if the karma is insufficient , it will not displayed as emoticon in plurk )


